c74object.name: seq.swing~

attribute.name: subdiv
attribute.digest: The number of segments the input phasor will be divided into before swing is applied to every other segment

attribute.name: depth
attribute.digest: Amount of swing to apply to the input phasor.

c74object.description: Swing is a clock modifier that creates a “swing” or “shuffle” rhythmic feel.
c74object.digest: Create variations in a ramp's slope for shuffle.
